  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Kōsoku Clan, Level <br />Your quick natured chakra imposes a subtle but meaningful effect against creatures who's speed is simply not up to par with your own. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Intelligence or Dexterity score by +1, up to the maximum of 20.</li><li>Hostile creatures within 20 feet of you, that have their movement speed reduced by a jutsu or feature, have their movement speed reduced further by half of their total movement speed reduction. If this would cause a creature's movement speed to go below half their maximum, their speed is instead reduced by 10ft (Min. 5).</li><li>You can learn and create Kōsoku Hijutsu in half the required time.</li></ul>",
